INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I had this dream, and I really wanted to be a star. And I was almost a monster in the way that I was really fearless with my ambitions.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I am a walking piece of art every day, with my dreams and my ambitions forward at all times in an effort to inspire my fans to lead their life in that way.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I don''t see myself in terms of artifice. I see myself as a real person who chooses to live my life in an open way - artistically.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I don''t think I could live without hair, makeup and styling, let alone be the performer I am. I am a glamour girl through and through. I believe in the glamorous life and I live one.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I talk about myself in the third person all the time. I don''t live my life in the way someone like you does. I live my life completely serving only my work and my fans.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I work very hard, but when God opens that door for you - when life opens that door for you, I should say - I think it''s important to be giving, to return the love back.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','It''s hard knowing who to trust with your personal life. When you cry in your room at night, you don''t always know who to call. So I am very close to my family.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','''Born this Way'' is about being yourself, and loving who you are and being proud.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','A record deal doesn''t make you an artist; you make yourself an artist.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I am so excited to extend myself behind the scenes as a designer and to - as my father puts it - finally have a real job.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I don''t like Los Angeles. The people are awful and terribly shallow, and everybody wants to be famous but nobody wants to play the game. I''m from New York. I will kill to get what I need.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I like pushing boundaries.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I want my fans to love themselves. It''s almost like I want to hypnotize them so when they hear my music they love themselves instantly.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I was performing in New York and my friends started to call me Gaga, they said I was very theatrical and they said, ''You''re Gaga''.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I''m definitely a Polaroid camera girl. For me, what I''m really excited about is bringing back the artistry and the nature of Polaroid.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','I''ve had grand pianos that are more expensive than, like, a year''s worth of rent.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','What I''ve learned is that you really don''t need to be a celebrity or have money or have the paparazzi following you around to be famous.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','When you''re around me and really see that all I do is live and breathe for my work, it''s not strange, it''s just Gaga.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lady Gaga','Where I come from it was really unheard of to be at a party and someone says, ''What kind of music do you make?'', and you say, ''Pop music.'' You may as well have ''I''m not cool'' stamped on your forehead.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','A good traveler has no fixed plans, and is not intent on arriving.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','A leader is best when people barely know he exists, when his work is done, his aim fulfilled, they will say: we did it ourselves.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','A scholar who cherishes the love of comfort is not fit to be deemed a scholar.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','All difficult things have their origin in that which is easy, and great things in that which is small.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Anticipate the difficult by managing the easy.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','At the center of your being you have the answer; you know who you are and you know what you want.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Be Content with what you have; rejoice in the way things are. When you realize there is nothing lacking, the whole world belongs to you.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Be the chief but never the lord.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Because of a great love, one is courageous.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Being deeply loved by someone gives you strength, while loving someone deeply gives you courage.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','By letting it go it all gets done. The world is won by those who let it go. But when you try and try. The world is beyond the winning.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Do the difficult things while they are easy and do the great things while they are small. A journey of a thousand miles must begin with a single step.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Fill your bowl to the brim and it will spill. Keep sharpening your knife and it will blunt.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','For the wise man looks into space and he knows there is no limited dimensions.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Govern a great nation as you would cook a small fish. Do not overdo it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Governing a great nation is like cooking a small fish - too much handling will spoil it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Great acts are made up of small deeds.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Great indeed is the sublimity of the Creative, to which all beings owe their beginning and which permeates all heaven.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','He who conquers others is strong; He who conquers himself is mighty.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','He who controls others may be powerful, but he who has mastered himself is mightier still.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','He who does not trust enough, Will not be trusted.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','He who is contented is rich.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','He who knows himself is enlightened.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','He who knows others is wise. He who knows himself is enlightened.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','He who knows that enough is enough will always have enough.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','He who knows, does not speak. He who speaks, does not know.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','He who obtains has little. He who scatters has much.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','He who talks more is sooner exhausted.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Health is the greatest possession. Contentment is the greatest treasure. Confidence is the greatest friend. Non-being is the greatest joy.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','How could man rejoice in victory and delight in the slaughter of men?');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','I have just three things to teach: simplicity, patience, compassion. These three are your greatest treasures.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','If you do not change direction, you may end up where you are heading.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','If you realize that all things change, there is nothing you will try to hold on to. If you are not afraid of dying, there is nothing you cannot achieve.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','If you would take, you must first give, this is the beginning of intelligence.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','In the world there is nothing more submissive and weak than water. Yet for attacking that which is hard and strong nothing can surpass it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','It is better to do one''s own duty, however defective it may be, than to follow the duty of another, however well one may perform it. He who does his duty as his own nature reveals it, never sins.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Kindness in words creates confidence. Kindness in thinking creates profoundness. Kindness in giving creates love.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Knowing others is wisdom, knowing yourself is Enlightenment.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Life is a series of natural and spontaneous changes. Don''t resist them - that only creates sorrow. Let reality be reality. Let things flow naturally forward in whatever way they like.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Love is of all passions the strongest, for it attacks simultaneously the head, the heart and the senses.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Man''s enemies are not demons, but human beings like himself.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Mastering others is strength. Mastering yourself is true power.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Nature does not hurry, yet everything is accomplished.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Nothing is softer or more flexible than water, yet nothing can resist it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Of all that is good, sublimity is supreme. Succeeding is the coming together of all that is beautiful. Furtherance is the agreement of all that is just. Perseverance is the foundation of all actions.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','One can not reflect in streaming water. Only those who know internal peace can give it to others.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','One who is too insistent on his own views, finds few to agree with him.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','People in their handlings of affairs often fail when they are about to succeed. If one remains as careful at the end as he was at the beginning, there will be no failure.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Respond intelligently even to unintelligent treatment.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Silence is a source of great strength.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','The higher the sun ariseth, the less shadow doth he cast; even so the greater is the goodness, the less doth it covet praise; yet cannot avoid its rewards in honours.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','The journey of a thousand miles begins with one step.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','The more laws and order are made prominent, the more thieves and robbers there will be.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','The people are hungry: It is because those in authority eat up too much in taxes.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','The snow goose need not bathe to make itself white. Neither need you do anything but be yourself.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','The softest things in the world overcome the hardest things in the world.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','The wicked leader is he who the people despise. The good leader is he who the people revere. The great leader is he who the people say, ''We did it ourselves.''');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','The wise man does not lay up his own treasures. The more he gives to others, the more he has for his own.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Those who have knowledge, don''t predict. Those who predict, don''t have knowledge.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','To the mind that is still, the whole universe surrenders.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Truthful words are not beautiful; beautiful words are not truthful. Good words are not persuasive; persuasive words are not good.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Violence, even well intentioned, always rebounds upon oneself.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','When I let go of what I am, I become what I might be.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','When you are content to be simply yourself and don''t compare or compete, everybody will respect you.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lao Tzu','Without stirring abroad, One can know the whole world; Without looking out of the window One can see the way of heaven. The further one goes The less one knows.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','Art is not a handicraft, it is the transmission of feeling the artist has experienced.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','To say that a work of art is good, but incomprehensible to the majority of men, is the same as saying of some kind of food that it is very good but that most people can''t eat it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','In the name of God, stop a moment, cease your work, look around you.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','All violence consists in some people forcing others, under threat of suffering or death, to do what they do not want to do.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','We lost because we told ourselves we lost.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','All happy families resemble one another, each unhappy family is unhappy in its own way.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','One of the first conditions of happiness is that the link between Man and Nature shall not be broken.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','Faith is the sense of life, that sense by virtue of which man does not destroy himself, but continues to live on. It is the force whereby we live.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','The changes in our life must come from the impossibility to live otherwise than according to the demands of our conscience not from our mental resolution to try a new form of life.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','The sole meaning of life is to serve humanity.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','True life is lived when tiny changes occur.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','Without knowing what I am and why I am here, life is impossible.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','All, everything that I understand, I understand only because I love.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','And all people live, Not by reason of any care they have for themselves, But by the love for them that is in other people.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','Everyone thinks of changing the world, but no one thinks of changing himself.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','There is no greatness where there is no simplicity, goodness and truth.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','Truth, like gold, is to be obtained not by its growth, but by washing away from it all that is not gold.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leo Tolstoy','The two most powerful warriors are patience and time.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','Simplicity is the ultimate sophistication.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','Where the spirit does not work with the hand, there is no art.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','I have been impressed with the urgency of doing. Knowing is not enough; we must apply. Being willing is not enough; we must do.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','He who is fixed to a star does not change his mind');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','He who loves practice without theory is like the sailor who boards ship without a rudder and compass and never knows where he may cast.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','Learning never exhausts the mind.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','Although nature commences with reason and ends in experience it is necessary for us to do the opposite, that is to commence with experience and from this to proceed to investigate the reason.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','As a well-spent day brings happy sleep, so a life well spent brings happy death.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','In rivers, the water that you touch is the last of what has passed and the first of that which comes; so with present time.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','While I thought that I was learning how to live, I have been learning how to die.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','Life is pretty simple: You do some stuff. Most fails. Some works. You do more of what works. If it works big, others quickly copy it. Then you do something else. The trick is the doing something else.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','For once you have tasted flight you will walk the earth with your eYes turned skywards, for there you have been and there you will long to return.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','It had long since come to my attention that people of accomplishment rarely sat back and let things happen to them. They went out and happened to things.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','Beyond a doubt truth bears the same relation to falsehood as light to darkness.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','Blinding ignorance does mislead us. O! Wretched mortals, open your eYes!');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','Human subtlety will never devise an invention more beautiful, more simple or more direct than does nature because in her inventions nothing is lacking, and nothing is superfluous.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','The greatest deception men suffer is from their own opinions.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','He who wishes to be rich in a day will be hanged in a year.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Leonardo da Vinci','The noblest pleasure is the joy of understanding.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','They never fail who die in a great cause.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Why I came here, I know not; where I shall go it is useless to inquire - in the midst of myriads of the living and the dead worlds, stars, systems, infinity, why should I be anxious about an atom?');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Love will find a way through paths where wolves fear to prey.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','This man is freed from servile bands, Of hope to rise, or fear to fall; Lord of himself, though not of lands, And leaving nothing, yet hath all.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Every day confirms my opinion on the superiority of a vicious life - and if Virtue is not its own reward I don''t know any other stipend annexed to it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','For in itself a thought, a slumbering thought, is capable of years, and curdles a long life into one hour.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Like the measles, love is most dangerous when it comes late in life.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Man''s love is of man''s life a part; it is a woman''s whole existence. In her first passion, a woman loves her lover, in all the others all she loves is love.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','The great art of life is sensation, to feel that we exist, even in pain.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','The poor dog, in life the firmest friend. The first to welcome, foremost to defend.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','What is the worst of woes that wait on age? What stamps the wrinkle deeper on the brow? To view each loved one blotted from life''s page, And be alone on earth, as I am now.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','A mistress never is nor can be a friend. While you agree, you are lovers; and when it is over, anything but friends.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Adversity is the first path to truth.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','All who joy would win must share it. Happiness was born a Twin.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Always laugh when you can. It is cheap medicine.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','As long as I retain my feeling and my passion for Nature, I can partly soften or subdue my other passions and resist or endure those of others.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','But what is Hope? Nothing but the paint on the face of Existence; the least touch of truth rubs it off, and then we see what a hollow-cheeked harlot we have got hold of.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Fame is the thirst of youth.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','For pleasures past I do not grieve, nor perils gathering near; My greatest grief is that I leave nothing that claims a tear.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','For truth is always strange; stranger than fiction.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Friendship is Love without his wings!');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Friendship may, and often does, grow into love, but love never subsides into friendship.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','He who is only just is cruel. Who on earth could live were all judged justly?');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','He who surpasses or subdues mankind, must look down on the hate of those below.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','I am about to be married, and am of course in all the misery of a man in pursuit of happiness.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','I do detest everything which is not perfectly mutual.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','I have great hopes that we shall love each other all our lives as much as if we had never married at all.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','I have no consistency, except in politics; and that probably arises from my indifference to the subject altogether.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','I love not man the less, but Nature more.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','I only go out to get me a fresh appetite for being alone.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','I should be very willing to redress men wrongs, and rather check than punish crimes, had not Cervantes, in that all too true tale of Quixote, shown how all such efforts fail.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','If I could always read, I should never feel the want of company.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','If I don''t write to empty my mind, I go mad.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','If we must have a tyrant, let him at least be a gentleman who has been bred to the business, and let us fall by the axe and not by the butcher''s cleaver.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','It is odd but agitation or contest of any kind gives a rebound to my spirits and sets me up for a time.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','It is useless to tell one not to reason but to believe - you might as well tell a man not to wake but sleep.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Let none think to fly the danger for soon or late love is his own avenger.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Lovers may be - and indeed generally are - enemies, but they never can be friends, because there must always be a spice of jealousy and a something of Self in all their speculations.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Man is born passionate of body, but with an innate though secret tendency to the love of Good in his main-spring of Mind. But God help us all! It is at present a sad jar of atoms.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Men think highly of those who rise rapidly in the world; whereas nothing rises quicker than dust, straw, and feathers.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','My turn of mind is so given to taking things in the absurd point of view, that it breaks out in spite of me every now and then.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Prolonged endurance tames the bold.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Smiles form the channels of a future tear.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Sometimes we are less unhappy in being deceived by those we love, than in being undeceived by them.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','The beginning of atonement is the sense of its necessity.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','The busy have no time for tears.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','The Cardinal is at his wit''s end - it is true that he had not far to go.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','The heart will break, but broken live on.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','There is no instinct like that of the heart.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','There is something pagan in me that I cannot shake off. In short, I deny nothing, but doubt everything.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Those who will not reason, are bigots, those who cannot, are fools, and those who dare not, are slaves.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Though I love my country, I do not love my countrymen.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Tis pleasant, sure, to see one''s name in print. A book''s a book, although there''s nothing in ''t.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','To have joy one must share it. Happiness was born a twin.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','To withdraw myself from myself has ever been my sole, my entire, my sincere motive in scribbling at all.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','We are all selfish and I no more trust myself than others with a good motive.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lord Byron','Who tracks the steps of glory to the grave?');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','I think everyone should experience defeat at least once during their career. You learn a lot from it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','Don''t be a spectator, don''t let life pass you by.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','If you''re bored with life - you don''t get up every morning with a burning desire to do things - you don''t have enough goals.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','Life is ten percent what happens to you and ninety percent how you respond to it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','Do right. Do your best. Treat others as you want to be treated.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','How you respond to the challenge in the second half will determine what you become after the game, whether you are a winner or a loser.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','I never learn anything talking. I only learn things when I ask questions.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','If what you did Yesterday seems big, you haven''t done anything today.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','In the successful organization, no detail is too small to escape close attention.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','It is a fine thing to have ability, but the ability to discover ability in others is the true test.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','It''s not the load that breaks you down, it''s the way you carry it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','Motivation is simple. You eliminate those who are not motivated.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','No one has ever drowned in sweat.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','Show me someone who has done something worthwhile, and I''ll show you someone who has overcome adversity.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','The man who complains about the way the ball bounces is likely the one who dropped it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','When all is said and done, more is said than done.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','You''ll never get ahead of anyone as long as you try to get even with him.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lou Holtz','You''re never as good as everyone tells you when you win, and you''re never as bad as they say when you lose.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','The moon and other celestial bodies should be free for exploration and use by all countries. No country should be permitted to advance a claim of sovereignty.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','I''d rather give my life than be afraid to give it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Presidents quickly realize that while a single act might destroy the world they live in, no one single decision can make life suddenly better or can turn history around for the good.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','A man can take a little bourbon without getting drunk, but if you hold his mouth open and pour in a quart, he''s going to get sick on it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','A man without a vote is man without protection.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Any jackass can kick down a barn but it takes a good carpenter to build one.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Did you ever think that making a speech on economics is a lot like pissing down your leg? It seems hot to you, but it never does to anyone else.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Doing what''s right isn''t the problem. It is knowing what''s right.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Education is not a problem. Education is an opportunity.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Freedom is not enough.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','I am making a collection of the things my opponents have found me to be and, when this election is over, I am going to open a museum and put them on display.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','I have learned that only two things are necessary to keep one''s wife happy. First, let her think she''s having her own way. And second, let her have it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','I report to you that our country is challenged at home and abroad: that it is our will that is being tried and not our strength; our sense of purpose and not our ability to achieve a better America.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','I want to make a policy statement. I am unabashedly in favor of women.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','I will do my best. That is all I can do. I ask for your help - and God''s.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','I''m tired. I''m tired of feeling rejected by the American people. I''m tired of waking up in the middle of the night worrying about the war.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','If one morning I walked on top of the water across the Potomac River, the headline that afternoon would read: "President Can''t Swim."');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','If two men agree on everything, you may be sure that one of them is doing the thinking.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','If you let a bully come in your front yard, he''ll be on your porch the next day and the day after that he''ll rape your wife in your own bed.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','It is always a strain when people are being killed. I don''t think anybody has held this job who hasn''t felt personally responsible for those being killed.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Jack was out kissing babies while I was out passing bills. Someone had to tend the store.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Jerry Ford is so dumb he can''t fart and chew gum at the same time.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','John F. Kennedy was the victim of the hate that was a part of our country. It is a disease that occupies the minds of the few but brings danger to the many.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','One lesson you better learn if you want to be in politics is that you never go out on a golf course and beat the President.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Only two things are necessary to keep one''s wife happy. One is to let her think she is having her own way, and the other is to let her have it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Our most tragic error may have been our inability to establish a rapport and a confidence with the press and television with the communication media. I don''t think the press has understood me.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Peace is a journey of a thousand miles and it must be taken one step at a time.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Poverty must not be a bar to learning and learning must offer an escape from poverty.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','The atomic bomb certainly is the most powerful of all weapons, but it is conclusively powerful and effective only in the hands of the nation which controls the sky.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','The fact that a man is a newspaper reporter is evidence of some flaw of character.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','The fifth freedom is freedom from ignorance.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','The guns and the bombs, the rockets and the warships, are all symbols of human failure.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','The noblest search is the search for excellence.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','The presidency has made every man who occupied it, no matter how small, bigger than he was; and no matter how big, not big enough for its demands.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','The separation of church and state is a source of strength, but the conscience of our nation does not call for separation between men of state and faith in the Supreme Being.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','The vote is the most powerful instrument ever devised by man for breaking down injustice and destroying the terrible walls which imprison men because they are different from other men.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','There are no problems we cannot solve together, and very few that we can solve by ourselves.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','There are plenty of recommendations on how to get out of trouble cheaply and fast. Most of them come down to this: Deny your responsibility.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','To conclude that women are unfitted to the task of our historic society seems to me the equivalent of closing male eYes to female facts.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Until justice is blind to color, until education is unaware of race, until opportunity is unconcerned with the color of men''s skins, emancipation will be a proclamation but not a fact.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','We have the opportunity to move not only toward the rich society and the powerful society, but upward to the Great Society.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','We must open the doors of opportunity. But we must also equip our people to walk through those doors.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','When I was young, poverty was so common that we didn''t know it had a name.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','When the burdens of the presidency seem unusually heavy, I always remind myself it could be worse. I could be a mayor.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','When things haven''t gone well for you, call in a secretary or a staff man and chew him out. You will sleep better and they will appreciate the attention.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Whether we are New Dealer, Old Dealer, Liberty Leaguer or Red, whether we agree or not, we still have the right to think and speak how we feel.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','While you''re saving your face, you''re losing your ass.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Whoever won''t fight when the President calls him, deserves to be kicked back in his hole and kept there.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','Yesterday is not ours to recover, but tomorrow is ours to win or lose.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','You aren''t learning anything when you''re talking.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','You do not examine legislation in the light of the benefits it will convey if properly administered, but in the light of the wrongs it would do and the harms it would cause if improperly administered.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Lyndon B Johnson','You''ve got to work things out in the cloakroom, and when you''ve got them worked out, you can debate a little before you vote.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mae West','Anything worth doing is worth doing slowly.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mae West','Between two evils, I always pick the one I never tried before.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mae West','You only live once, but if you do it right, once is enough');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mae West','It''s not what I do, but the way I do it. It''s not what I say, but the way I say it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mae West','The score never interested me, only the game.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mae West','It''s not the men in my life that count, it''s the life in my men.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Maharishi Mahesh Yogi','Whatever we put our attention on will grow stronger in our life.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Maharishi Mahesh Yogi','I let people make remarks about me, but it doesn''t touch me, all those remarks.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Maharishi Mahesh Yogi','The important thing is this: to be able, at any moment, to sacrifice what we are for what we could become.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Faith... must be enforced by reason... when faith becomes blind it dies.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I am prepared to die, but there is no cause for which I am prepared to kill.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I believe that a man is the strongest soldier for daring to die unarmed.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Let us all be brave enough to die the death of a martyr, but let no one lust for martyrdom.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Live as if you were to die tomorrow. Learn as if you were to live forever.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Man lives freely only by his readiness to die, if need be, at the hands of his brother, never by killing him.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Violent men have not been known in history to die to a man. They die up to a point.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','What difference does it make to the dead, the orphans, and the homeless, whether the mad destruction is wrought under the name of totalitarianism or the holy name of liberty or democracy?');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Fear has its use but cowardice has none.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Only he can take great resolves who has indomitable faith in God and has fear of God.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','A ''No'' uttered from the deepest conviction is better than a ''Yes'' merely uttered to please, or worse, to avoid trouble.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','A man is but the product of his thoughts what he thinks, he becomes.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','A man who was completely innocent, offered himself as a sacrifice for the good of others, including his enemies, and became the ransom of the world. It was a perfect act.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','A principle is the expression of perfection, and as imperfect beings like us cannot practise perfection, we devise every moment limits of its compromise in practice.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','A vow is a purely religious act which cannot be taken in a fit of passion. It can be taken only with a mind purified and composed and with God as witness.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','A weak man is just by accident. A strong but non-violent man is unjust by accident.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Action expresses priorities.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','All compromise is based on give and take, but there can be no give and take on fundamentals. Any compromise on mere fundamentals is a surrender. For it is all give and no take.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','All the religions of the world, while they may differ in other respects, unitedly proclaim that nothing lives in this world but Truth.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','An eye for an eye only ends up making the whole world blind.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','An ounce of practice is worth more than tons of preaching.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Anger and intolerance are the enemies of correct understanding.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Anger is the enemy of non-violence and pride is a monster that swallows it up.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Are creeds such simple things like the clothes which a man can change at will and put on at will? Creeds are such for which people live for ages and ages.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','As human beings, our greatness lies not so much in being able to remake the world - that is the myth of the atomic age - as in being able to remake ourselves.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Before the throne of the Almighty, man will be judged not by his acts but by his intentions. For God alone reads our hearts.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','But for my faith in God, I should have been a raving maniac.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Confession of errors is like a broom which sweeps away the dirt and leaves the surface brighter and clearer. I feel stronger for confession.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Constant development is the law of life, and a man who always tries to maintain his dogmas in order to appear consistent drives himself into a false position.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Each one has to find his peace from within. And peace to be real must be unaffected by outside circumstances.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Each one prays to God according to his own light.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Even if you are a minority of one, the truth is the truth.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Everyone who wills can hear the inner voice. It is within everyone.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','First they ignore you, then they laugh at you, then they fight you, then you win.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Freedom is never dear at any price. It is the breath of life. What would a man not pay for living?');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Gentleness, self-sacrifice and generosity are the exclusive possession of no one race or religion.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Glory lies in the attempt to reach one''s goal and not in reaching it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','God is, even though the whole world deny him. Truth stands, even if there be no public support. It is self-sustained.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','God sometimes does try to the uttermost those whom he wishes to bless.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','God, as Truth, has been for me a treasure beyond price. May He be so to every one of us.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Honest disagreement is often a good sign of progress.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I claim that human mind or human society is not divided into watertight compartments called social, political and religious. All act and react upon one another.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I claim to be a simple individual liable to err like any other fellow mortal. I own, however, that I have humility enough to confess my errors and to retrace my steps.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I do all the evil I can before I learn to shun it? Is it not enough to know the evil to shun it? If not, we should be sincere enough to admit that we love evil too well to give it up.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I do not want to foresee the future. I am concerned with taking care of the present. God has given me no control over the moment following.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I have also seen children successfully surmounting the effects of an evil inheritance. That is due to purity being an inherent attribute of the soul.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I have nothing new to teach the world. Truth and Non-violence are as old as the hills. All I have done is to try experiments in both on as vast a scale as I could.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I know, to banish anger altogether from one''s breast is a difficult task. It cannot be achieved through pure personal effort. It can be done only by God''s grace.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I look only to the good qualities of men. Not being faultless myself, I won''t presume to probe into the faults of others.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I object to violence because when it appears to do good, the good is only temporary; the evil it does is permanent.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I reject any religious doctrine that does not appeal to reason and is in conflict with morality.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','I will far rather see the race of man extinct than that we should become less than beasts by making the noblest of God''s creation, woman, the object of our lust.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','If co-operation is a duty, I hold that non-co-operation also under certain conditions is equally a duty.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','If I had no sense of humor, I would long ago have committed suicide.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','If patience is worth anything, it must endure to the end of time. And a living faith will last in the midst of the blackest storm.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','If we are to teach real peace in this world, and if we are to carry on a real war against war, we shall have to begin with the children.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Imitation is the sincerest flattery.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','In matters of conscience, the law of the majority has no place.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','In prayer it is better to have a heart without words than words without a heart.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Infinite striving to be the best is man''s duty; it is its own reward. Everything else is in God''s hands.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Interdependence is and ought to be as much the ideal of man as self-sufficiency. Man is a social being.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Intolerance betrays want of faith in one''s cause.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Intolerance is itself a form of violence and an obstacle to the growth of a true democratic spirit.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Is it not enough to know the evil to shun it? If not, we should be sincere enough to admit that we love evil too well to give it up.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','It has always been a mystery to me how men can feel themselves honoured by the humiliation of their fellow beings.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','It is any day better to stand erect with a broken and bandaged head then to crawl on one''s belly, in order to be able to save one''s head.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','It is better to be violent, if there is violence in our hearts, than to put on the cloak of nonviolence to cover impotence.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','It is easy enough to be friendly to one''s friends. But to befriend the one who regards himself as your enemy is the quintessence of true religion. The other is mere business.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','It is health that is real wealth and not pieces of gold and silver.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','It is the quality of our work which will please God and not the quantity.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','It is unwise to be too sure of one''s own wisdom. It is healthy to be reminded that the strongest might weaken and the wisest might err.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Just as a man would not cherish living in a body other than his own, so do nations not like to live under other nations, however noble and great the latter may be.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Justice that love gives is a surrender, justice that law gives is a punishment.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Let everyone try and find that as a result of daily prayer he adds something new to his life, something with which nothing can be compared.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Man should forget his anger before he lies down to sleep.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Man''s nature is not essentially evil. Brute nature has been know to yield to the influence of love. You must never despair of human nature.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Measures must always in a progressive society be held superior to men, who are after all imperfect instruments, working for their fulfilment.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Moral authority is never retained by any attempt to hold on to it. It comes without seeking and is retained without effort.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Morality which depends upon the helplessness of a man or woman has not much to recommend it. Morality is rooted in the purity of our hearts.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Nearly everything you do is of no importance, but it is important that you do it.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Nobody can hurt me without my permission.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Non-cooperation with evil is as much a duty as is cooperation with good.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Non-violence and truth are inseparable and presuppose one another.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Non-violence is not a garment to be put on and off at will. Its seat is in the heart, and it must be an inseparable part of our being.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Non-violence is the greatest force at the disposal of mankind. It is mightier than the mightiest weapon of destruction devised by the ingenuity of man.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','Non-violence requires a double faith, faith in God and also faith in man.');
INSERT INTO `QUOTES` (AUTHOR,QUOTE) VALUES ('Mahatma Gandhi','One''s own religion is after all a matter between oneself and one''s Maker and no one else''s.');
